Dialogs.Dialog: We're fine to go now. Where to？
I'm sorry, I have plans after returning home. Thank you for inviting me though.
I see. Well, at least let me take you home.
I see. Okay, then we'll go there.
Well, if you want to go...
It's okay, I have time today.
I'm sorry, I have something to do today. But, if we go home together...
Yeah, that's fine too. Let's go.
I agree with you. Then, let's go.
Do you want to go there？ Yeah, I don't think so.
I'm sure you'd enjoy it too, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Do you think it's a good idea？ Okay, I understand.
Please, not now. Right now it's... I'm sorry.
I don't want to go home today.
Okay, then let's take a detour.
I won't refuse anything you ask, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I'm sorry to hear that. There are days like that.
Don't apologize. Let's go home back together.
Oh, I'm sorry. I was about to go home！
Are you sure you'll do that？ You didn't forget it, did you？
I thought homeroom was taking too long, but... It wasn't that, was it？
If you have some time left, can I ask you something？
You came all the way here.
Because I wanted to see you soon.
Well, I'm going get going now.
Ah, you were here. Let's go, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hey, isn't it your turn today？ Did you erase the blackboard？
Well, you're fine. When I looked into the classroom, it was already clean.
(I didn't erase it... No way, did ▲高嶺＊＊▲...？)
Are you still in your classroom？
Yes, I'll go out now. Sorry.
Hey, it's your turn today, so write in the log and then you can go home.
I know... I'm sorry. Wait a second please, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hmm. Can I see how you do your chores today？
(That will only make my work a lot harder...)
Ah, it's my turn to do class chores. I still haven't written in the class log.
I'll be waiting for you, so write quickly.
Well, you know, I think I'll leave it like that. I'll write something tomorrow morning.
Really？ Then, let's review today's classes so you don't forget them, yes.
The first period was... What was it again？
Are you sure you want to do this tomorrow？
Hmm？ Ah, the Life Guidance sensei.
...Yes, I can't let him find me.
It's rare to see you hiding from a sensei, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
...Well, that's because that sensei likes to raise his voice while making fun of me.
How difficult did you feel the quiz was？
Emm... Let's not talk about that.
Hello. What are you talking about？
Hahaha, see you. Have your girlfriend comfort you！
Shut up！ Hurry up and go！
(I should keep quiet about the test.)
Oh, it's Takane's partner. Is it a date？
Yes, special training for doubles... I'm kidding.
If you make Takane cry, we won't forgive you！
I wonder what they could be planning？
(She has a lot fans... I think I have to be careful with you ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Oh, are you free right now？
I'm sorry, today is really not a good time.
I see, I understand. Why... only you. You are such a moron！
Why are you fighting？ What's the cause？
(It's hard to say it's because of you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
I'm sorry. Are you okay with that？
Oh, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. What are you doing？
Someone I don't know told me to give them my mail address. Of course, I refused.
(Having a cute girlfriend is a lot of work...)
I came to pick you up, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Thank you. Well then, let's go.
Yeah, I brought my dictionary. Today's class was in another room, so we only had 3 dictionaries.
(You bring your dictionary everyday... I expected nothing less of you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Are you okay？ I swing my bag too much.
Haha, when I saw you do that. I got nervous, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
▲主人公＊▲, I was waiting for you.
I see... But, how did you know I usually pass through here？
(Everything...？ I can't do anything wrong now.)
Sorry to keep you waiting, let's go.
Oh, you were running in the corridors...
Haha, that'd be a violation of the school rules.
It's dangerous, the floor is wet...
Does it hurt？ If you got hurt, we can't go on a date today.
It's dangerous if you run in the corridors. I won't go anywhere, but don't run in the corridors, okay？
I feel like I've forgotten something...
Eh, it can't be. Wait for me, I'll go get it right away！
(When you're careless like this, you're so cute ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！ I didn't notice you at all.
I'm sorry... I waved my hand, but you didn't notice me.
I wish I could talk to you more frequently.
So if I reach this point and call you, that means I've lost？ ...I'm kidding.
(Sometimes I wonder if you can makes jokes, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
▲主人公＊▲. I'm sorry, but you caught me at a bad time...
I saw a dog a while ago. I was looking for it.
(You were making funny noises for the doggy ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Can I ask you for a favor？
A favor？ What do you need？
I'd like you to give this letter to a boy in your class...
Yes, it's from one of my friends. Don't be so surprised, okay？
Excuse me... Is it true that you're dating Takane？
▲主人公＊▲. Was that a girl from the first year？ Do you know her？
Oh, you look cute when you are together like that.
Huh？ Is that a sensei with ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
The sensei asked me if "I was going on a date" right now... ▲主人公＊▲.
I'm sorry, did you wait for me that much ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
No, not at all. Okay, let's go.
Oh, today's mixed doubles look fine. Hahaha.
Hey, what does mixed doubles mean？
Yo, sorry to make you wait.
Go home early, so you don't make your family worry.
Alright. Well, if you're with Takane, then I won't worry that much.
(That thing Oyama said... You're amazing ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
(Huh, my wallet is not in my pocket.)
Sorry to keep you waiting. What are you looking for？
Oh, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. It looks like I've lost my wallet. Maybe dropped it...
I got you covered. Your friend asked me to give it to you.
Second year, Takane-san. Head to the staff room...
It's fine, you were called out. But why？
A sensei asked me to represent the second years at the school meeting.
So that was it. I thought they were angry at you.
Geez. I haven't done anything wrong.
(She's late. I wonder if I should send her an email to ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
(Hmm？ Is there something ringing behind me？)
A pity, you found me out. I wanted to scare you, but I failed.
I'm glad I send you that email.
Ah... Look over there, one of my classmates...
Hmm？ Oh, I've seen him before. Huh, is he dating someone now？
Yes, that's right... Hehe, it looks like he's having fun.
Then we can't lose to them！
Hmm... Did you know？ Girls immediately notice when you are looking at something.
When I'm dating with you, I remember when I was little and I used to play date with Papa...
That kind of parent-child date is cute. I bet the small you was cute, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
I misspoke, you are cute every time, over all, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Don't look at them, that's something bad.
I'm training everyday, so I'm more powerful than her, right？ ...I'm kidding.
(Even if I knew she was joking, I was scared...)
And you went and put trash away. I knew it, you're really amazing ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
It's not like that. I read in a book that the city is dirty because people throws more trash than people can pick.
I see, then we should help the people who picks up garbage.
Oh, there's something on your neck, lemme look at it.
Is that the name of the song I'm humming？
What do you know, you have perfect pitch too.
The man you were talking to... Were you playing a game？
Do you want try it together？ What kind of games do you like？
Well, I like nervous breakdown... Speed, that kind of thing？
(You need a game console for that...)
Huh, did you get one the flyers they were giving out？
It's sweet potato bread... It looks delicious, doesn't it？
Ah, it's Mama. She wrote, "Are you still on a date".
Hehe. I've said "I'm still with him", she said "I don't mind then, enjoy".
...Ah, it looks like it was a mistake. Sorry, were you surprised？
It's from Mama. I was asked to go shopping.
▲主人公＊▲. Wait, there's some lint on your clothes.
Oh, you also have some, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
This reminds me of the grooming some animals do.
Haha, it may be like that.
Hmmm, I don't remember if it's today...
No, I don't remember having anything planned. Maybe I've set something wrong.
Geez, are you sure you are alright？
Ah... A new product release at Winning Burger.
Is that the e-mail magazine？ You were using it before I knew it.
When you register, you get a discount coupon, isn't it amazing？
(I'm so proud of you... You are really cute ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
I have something in my eyes...
Hey, look over there. There is a couple kissing over there.
Huh！？ No！ This is something different！
(It looks like this, but it's something else.)
See you. I hope tomorrow will be like today, and tomorrow and the day after tomorrow.
I hope so too. See you tomorrow at school.
See you tomorrow. Don't be late.
Well then, see ya. Tomorrow's a day off, but you should do your homework tonight... I'm kidding.
See ya. Don't stay up late because you'll feel sleepy tomorrow.
Ah ▲高嶺＊＊▲, I... that's... Hmm, I'll be fine. See ya.
I'm feeling a little tired. I have an early start tomorrow and I want to relax. See you.
